    dc:description "Figure 2. Epeolus albus Astafurova & Proshchalykin, sp. nov., male, holotype (A-I), paratype (J) A-C habitus, lateral (A); dorsal (B) and ventral (C) views D head, frontal view E labrum, frontal view F pygidial plate, dorsal view G, H mesoscutellum, dorsolateral (G) and dorsal (H) views I hind basitarsus, lateral view J genitalia, dorsal view. Scale bars: 1.0 mm (A-C); 0.5 mm (D); 0.25 mm (E-J)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/917751" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

